controller

Class EditPhotoController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.EditPhotoController

  • public class EditPhotoController
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages procedures to edit a photo. Displays photo details and options to add, delete, or edit a tag. The user cannot edit the photo's file name, however.
    Author:
    Omar Khalil, Michelle Hwang
